continually developing and improving the services and features of our plugins. Despite UpdraftClone only being released a few weeks ago, we are thrilled to announce that we have already released &#8230; <a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftclone-update-now-allows-users-to-login-via-ssh/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">&#8594;</span></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftclone-update-now-allows-users-to-login-via-ssh/\">UpdraftClone update now allows users to login via SSH</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"wmullins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1591:\"<p>You all know by now that UpdraftPlus are committed to continually developing and improving the services and features of our plugins. Despite UpdraftClone only being released a few weeks ago, we are thrilled to announce that we have already released a new update in the form of users now being able to login via SSH in the browser.</p>\n<p>This update means that from today, once you boot up any new clones that you have created, you will find a SSH login link in your account clone list.This new feature gives you more control over your clones and allows you to login via SSH in the browser.</p>\n<p>We hope you enjoy this new feature. Be sure to visit UpdraftClone for further updates and information.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CloneBlog.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-313327\" src=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CloneBlog.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"648\" height=\"226\" srcset=\"https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CloneBlog.png 648w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CloneBlog-300x105.png 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CloneBlog-510x178.png 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftclone-update-now-allows-users-to-login-via-ssh/\">UpdraftClone update now allows users to login via SSH</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href=\"http://updraftplus.com\">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftclone-update-now-allows-users-to-login-via-ssh/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"https://updraftplus.com/updraftclone-update-now-allows-users-to-login-via-ssh/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"